            <title>[HBASE-10716] [Configuration]: hbase.regionserver.region.split.policy should be part of hbase-default.xml</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-10716</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The split policy is not being set in hbase-default.xml. Setting it will help the users to understand that it can be configurable. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
